# My Pi-Hole List

A simple tool to update your adlist. You can fork it and modify it.

## Requirements

- docker
- docker compose

## How to use

1. Fork the repo
2. `make pihole-adlist-builder` will create and run a container with all you need to develop and use this project. After the command you will be logged into che container.
3. `make build` will compose your new adlist file
